<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Personal Branding Kit</title>
    
    <!-- Tailwind CSS -->
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    
    <!-- Fonts Setup -->
    <!-- Google Fonts: Inter, IBM Plex Sans, Work Sans, Noto Sans KR -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=IBM+Plex+Sans:wght@300;400;600&family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;700&family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;500;700&family=Work+Sans:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <!-- Pretendard (via CDN) -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" as="style" crossorigin href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/orioncactus/pretendard@v1.3.9/dist/web/static/pretendard.css" />

    <!-- Icons (Lucide) -->
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/lucide@latest"></script>

    <style>
        /* Custom Font Classes matching the prompt */
        .font-set-a-en { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; }
        .font-set-a-kr { font-family: 'Pretendard', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, Roboto, sans-serif; }
        
        .font-set-b-en { font-family: 'IBM Plex Sans', sans-serif; }
        .font-set-b-kr { font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif; }
        
        .font-set-c-en { font-family: 'Work Sans', sans-serif; }
        .font-set-c-kr { font-family: 'Spoqa Han Sans Neo', 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif; } /* Fallback to Noto if Spoqa isn't loaded locally, but styling matches the vibe */

        /* Color Variables for easy reference within Tailwind config if needed, but used inline for clarity */
        :root {
            --bg-soft-ivory: #F6F3EE;
            --text-main: #151821;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--bg-soft-ivory);
            color: var(--text-main);
            font-family: 'Pretendard', 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif; /* Default fallback */
        }

        .color-card {
            transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
        }
        .color-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 4px 6px -2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }
        
        .toast {
            visibility: hidden;
            min-width: 250px;
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 16px;
            position: fixed;
            z-index: 50;
            left: 50%;
            bottom: 30px;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.3s, bottom 0.3s;
        }

        .toast.show {
            visibility: visible;
            opacity: 1;
            bottom: 50px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="antialiased min-h-screen flex flex-col">

    <!-- Toast Notification -->
    <div id="toast" class="toast shadow-lg">Hex Code Copied!</div>

    <!-- Header / Hero Section -->
    <header class="w-full py-16 px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-24 bg-[#F6F3EE] border-b border-[#D3B792]/30">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start md:items-end gap-6">
                <div>
                    <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 mb-4 text-xs font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-[#365A72] bg-[#365A72]/10 rounded-full">Brand Identity System</div>
                    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-[#20293A] tracking-tight mb-3">
                        Deep Focus & <span class="text-[#D67B68]">Warm Connection</span>
                    </h1>
                    <p class="text-lg text-[#4F7D73] max-w-2xl">
                        깊이 있는 분석과 따뜻한 스토리텔링이 만나는 지점. <br>
                        이성적인 구조 설계자와 감성적인 조율자를 위한 비주얼 가이드라인입니다.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="text-right hidden md:block">
                    <p class="text-sm text-[#23252B] opacity-60">Created for</p>
                    <p class="font-semibold text-[#151821]">Strategic Storyteller</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="flex-grow w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-24 py-12 space-y-20">

