                        </p>
                        <div class="flex gap-3">
                            <button class="px-4 py-2 bg-[#20293A] text-white rounded-md text-sm font-medium font-set-a-en">View Project</button>
                            <button class="px-4 py-2 bg-white border border-[#20293A] text-[#20293A] rounded-md text-sm font-medium font-set-a-kr">자세히 보기</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Set B -->
